Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan wins Republican nomination
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w2r8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Jul 1980
Republican convention endorses the nomination of 70-year-old Ronald Reagan as its presidential candidate. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less